<topic id="filters-author-outliner">
  <title>Outline Filters</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>XML Outline View<indexterm>Author<indexterm>outline
          filters</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The following actions are available in the <ph product="editor author"><image
          href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_ywb_d3m_ks"/><uicontrol>Settings</uicontrol> menu
        of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view</ph><ph product="editorEclipse authorEclipse"
          ><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol> of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view</ph> when
      editing in <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode:<dl id="ouline-filters-dl">
        <dlentry id="filter-returns-exact-dlentry">
          <dt><uicontrol>Filter returns exact matches</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The text filter of the <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view returns only exact
            matches.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="outline-flat-presentation-mode"
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline-flat-presentation-mode">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_show_comments">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/show_element_name">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/comments_sjow_text">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_show_attributes">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/OptionsShortcut16.gif" id="image_gtn_mmm_ks"/>Configure
              displayed attributes</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Displays the <xref href="preferences-outline.dita#preferences-outline" format="dita"
              >XML Structured Outline preferences page</xref>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <p id="outliner-filter-box">The upper part of the view contains a filter box which allows you to
      focus on the relevant components. Type a text fragment in the filter box and only the
      components that match it are presented. For advanced usage you can use wildcard characters (*,
      ?) and separate multiple patterns with commas.</p>
